Property of BTS is all right subtrees of root will have greater value than root and all left subtrees of root will have lesser value than root.

Common ancestor will justify this condition p.val < root.val > q.val

So if p.val < root.val and q.val < root.val,
move root to its left i.e root=root.left

So if p.val > root.val and q.val > root.val,
move root to its right i.e root=root.right

else we have our root ancestor


